longBusinessSummary: Infinity Energy Resources, Inc. focuses on the acquisition, exploration, and development of oil and gas resources. It has an option to acquire oil and gas properties in central Kansas covering an area of approximately 11,000 acres. Infinity Energy Resources, Inc. was incorporated in 1987 and is based in Overland Park, Kansas.
